name: experiment 4
description:
made by manually arranging rows of pixels in a pattern of red/black/green/black/blue/black and red,white/green/white/blue/white and moving the pixels up/down/left/right in a weaving motion every frame.
Because it was made manually by a human, there are some human errors.

32 x 32, 70 frames, 12fps.
artist: @mumu_thestan
